# 3.1.1.research.external.q1.rate-limit-http-code

## question

what http status code does claude api return when subscription hits rate limit?

## options

- 401 unauthorized (auth-like error)
- 429 too many requests (explicit rate limit)
- other?

## why it matters

determines how `isAuthPoolTokenRateLimited` detects exhaustion.

## research approach

check claude cli error handle logic, anthropic api docs, or test empirically.

## .status

awaited
